@startuml
title Group Chat — Deployment Diagram
skinparam linetype ortho

node "Server Host" {
  artifact "TCPServer.jar" as Server
  artifact "server.properties\n(host / port)" as SCfg
  Server ..> SCfg : reads at runtime
}

node "Client Host A" {
  artifact "TCPClient.jar" as ClientA
}
node "Client Host B" {
  artifact "TCPClient.jar" as ClientB
}
node "Client Host C\n(read-only guest)" {
  artifact "TCPClient.jar" as ClientC
}

ClientA --> Server : TCP/IP socket : 3000
ClientB --> Server : TCP/IP socket : 3000
ClientC --> Server : TCP/IP socket : 3000

note bottom of Server
  Thread-per-connection:
  one ClientHandler thread per client.
end note
@enduml
